{"tid":1534764,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"物業管理公司質素","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:16:51.000Z","uid":295256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"166357f621108b9cc0f17bcd8fdbdb27782f9052","tid":1534764,"uid":295256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"小弟大厦要轉管理....求巴𢇁比吓意見<br />\n（唔想pick咗紅底or藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n羅富樓宇官理<br />\n港深聨合物業管理<br />\n柏齡物業管理<br />\n威格斯物業管理<br />\n至興物業管理<br />\n富寧物業管理<br />\n九源物業管理<br />\n其士富居物業管理"},{"pid":"b09fe8e86fa20124de879ff924298140f249aef1","tid":1534764,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d80765544829121b747863dce5bc06943888b8ae","tid":1534764,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"e094dc9be363623ba0be3262ea9191c108bf7cad","tid":1534764,"uid":266354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"166357f621108b9cc0f17bcd8fdbdb27782f9052","tid":1534764,"uid":295256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"小弟大厦要轉管理....求巴𢇁比吓意見<br />\n（唔想pick咗紅底or藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n羅富樓宇官理<br />\n港深聨合物業管理<br />\n柏齡物業管理<br />\n威格斯物業管理<br />\n至興物業管理<br />\n富寧物業管理<br />\n九源物業管理<br />\n其士富居物業管理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"九源係工聯會渣旗 其他等補充"},{"pid":"0fb5f6c4d9889fd0f7aac8a694c4e06cd9dc54b4","tid":1534764,"uid":295256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e094dc9be363623ba0be3262ea9191c108bf7cad","tid":1534764,"uid":266354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"166357f621108b9cc0f17bcd8fdbdb27782f9052","tid":1534764,"uid":2